  "id": "019d286a-f2d8-78b2-92cd-5772cb4d5e00",
  "content": "### Triple Role\n### Repository Structure\n\n### Demo Config\n\n```toml\n[project]\nname = \"corvia-demo\"\nscope_id = \"corvia\"\n\n[workspace]\nrepos_dir = \"repos\"\n\n[[workspace.repos]]\nname = \"corvia\"\nurl = \"https://github.com/<org>/corvia\"\nnamespace = \"kernel\"\n\n[[workspace.repos]]\nname = \"corvia-adapter-git\"\nurl = \"https://github.com/<org>/corvia-adapter-git\"\nnamespace = \"adapter\"\n\n[storage]\nstore_type = \"lite\"\ndata_dir = \".corvia\"\n\n[embedding]\nprovider = \"ollama\"\nmodel = \"nomic-embed-text\"\nurl = \"http://127.0.0.1:11434\"\ndimensions = 768\n\n[server]\nhost = \"127.0.0.1\"\nport = 8020\n```\n\n\n### Devcontainer\n\n```jsonc\n{\n  \"name\": \"Corvia Demo Workspace\",\n  \"build\": { \"dockerfile\": \"Dockerfile\" },\n  \"postCreateCommand\": \".devcontainer/scripts/post-create.sh\",\n  \"postStartCommand\": \".devcontainer/scripts/post-start.sh\",\n  \"forwardPorts\": [8020],\n  \"customizations\": {\n    \"vscode\": {\n      \"extensions\": [],\n      \"settings\": {\n        \"corvia.serverUrl\": \"http://localhost:8020\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Lifecycle**:\n- `postCreate`: `corvia workspace init` (clones repos, pulls Ollama model if missing)\n- `postStart`: `corvia serve --mcp &` (background server)\n- Pre-ingested knowledge means instant search without waiting for embedding\n",
